data.description: THIS HOUSE IS READY FOR you. Lots of space, lots of closets and lots of storage. It features a freshly upgraded family playroom with real wood floors upstairs and brick floors in kitchen and den. All within minutes of midtown attractions, this beautiful, spacious home in McGehee Estates is ready for you to move in. It features over 3000 square feet with beautiful mature tees in a wonderful neighborhood. This home is also priced to sell. This house would be perfect for a family to come move in like it is or add some upgrades and this houses value will shoot up. This house had 1 owner who had it built. It is sturdy and solid and waiting on you. Seller is now  offering a $10,000 Decorator Allowance. Just think about what you can do with this!!
